         <image src="../webcontent/didigetthis_linear8_02.gif" alt="graph with liner equation y=5096-491x"/>
         <p>In the <?oxy_comment_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101101T184139-0400" comment="Suggest changing above image so that the equation reads &quot;Y = 5096 + (-491)X"?>above
               image<?oxy_comment_end?>, what is the slope of the regression line?</p>
      </body>
